---
import ContentLayout from '@layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---
<ContentLayout title="Partner Drills" eyebrow="Practice" description="Cooperative partner formats for safe grip, lock, and posture feedback." breadcrumbs={[{ label: 'Practice', href: '/practice/' }, { label: 'Partner Drills' }]}>
  <h2>Outside Sleeve 1 Cooperative Drill</h2>
  <h3>Purpose</h3>
  <p>Train the entry, hand capture, and gradual pressure without resistance.</p>
  <h3>Starting position</h3>
  <p>Uke takes a realistic outside sleeve grip. Nage begins relaxed and balanced.</p>
  <h3>Defender role</h3>
  <p>Move slowly through the entry, pause at the control point, and add pressure only until posture changes.</p>
  <h3>Uke role</h3>
  <p>Keep a realistic but safe grip, move with pressure, and tap early.</p>
  <h3>Safety</h3>
  <p>Tap early. Move with pressure. Do not resist suddenly.</p>
  <h3>Progression</h3>
  <ol><li>Static grip.</li><li>Light resistance.</li><li>Add footwork.</li><li>Add controlled takedown only if safe.</li></ol>
</ContentLayout>
